{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"中国共产党三十年","authors":["黄炎培"],"dates":[{"year":1951,"month":7,"day":2}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党三十年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄炎培"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大！伟大！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光普遍地照耀在百姓之家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜蜜蜜地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暖和和地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一齐倒在母亲之怀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还堪回忆么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无情的风猛吹着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨猛打着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可怜而又可爱的这民主的嫩芽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真欣幸的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么路线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中间有些，也许认为这样地干，是有效的贡献。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失败了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失败了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒积下了不少经验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到底真理给哲人发现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理是早给哲人发见了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无奈一时还没有成熟的条件。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去若干重要关头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到今朝都值得大大地纪念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最值得纪念的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一九三五年遵义一场会议，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才在思想上在领导上得到了正确的基本的改变。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事情已经很急迫了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣幸！欣幸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于获得一致的觉悟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一致的拥护，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"证明了真理普遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人，一年比一年加多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力，一年比一年加强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些是自然的了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难得的，是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"质，一年比一年加良。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是偶然的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对人要和大众紧密联系，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对己要自我批评；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些武器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会从人群中放出万丈光芒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有流水是不腐的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事实已经证明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不是夸张。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到今天，我识得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当时延安一席谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我估计过低了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所得到的答复，是正确的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“只有人人起来负责，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这好政府才会久长。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很宝贵的发现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是人民民主统一战线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人阶级领导问题解决了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农联盟问题解决了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发现了它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使党和革命更得到迅速的发展。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中间的一点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国资产阶级，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有两个不同的集团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其中一个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族资产阶级，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是可以争取的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只须有一定的条件，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能认做敌人危险。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些有他的基本观点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“马列主义中国化了。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请读又深刻又通俗的哲学文章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"论实践。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说不尽的折磨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“中华人民共和国”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用什么铸成的？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是千千万万人民英雄们之血。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从第一次到第五次围攻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大渡河的水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原的雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深地印在上边的是什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二万五千里长征脚迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更经过了八年间一面和国内反动派斗争，一面抗日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切的一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记也记不清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写也写不完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“即使把天下的树都变成笔”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“红旗漫卷西风”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们被叫醒了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在长期沉睡中；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被鼓舞了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"环绕在它周围的大大小小不同民族的革命运动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是强大无比的人民民主堡垒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是精锐无比的人民革命先锋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗美援朝，是它向帝国主义胜利地英勇地进攻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它之所以成功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它把政治思想渗透在以工农为主要成分的军队中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它掌握了新民主主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它发挥了新民主主义下的种种作风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大！伟大！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界每一个角落在歌颂着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“中国出了一个毛泽东！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年七月一日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}